Revision of an extraordinary Selizini genus Urana Melichar, 1902 from Madagascar (Hemiptera: Fulgoromorpha: Flatidae)This paper revises an extraordinary Madagascan genus Urana Melichar, 1902, with two species Urana paradoxa Melichar, 1902 and Urana unica sp. nov. The genus represents the tribe Selizini of the subfamily Flatinae. Additionally, distribution of the genus is discussed.